<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70AA506019" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Zamjena baterije daljinskog upravljača
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite ključ za slučaj nužde (4).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite gornje kućište (1) pomoću plosnatog odvijača kao što je prikazano na slici.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite tiskanu ploču (2) s donjeg kućišta (3).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW101A50043.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "73.205mm" ver = "01" gw = "163" gh = "191"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.291in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.847in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
5.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Krpa
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite bateriju (2) pomoću plosnatog odvijača (1) kako je prikazano na slici.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW101A50044.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "32.419mm" ver = "01" gw = "169" gh = "75"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.125in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Krpa
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite bateriju (dugmasta litijska CR 2032 ili baterija jednakih svojstava) (1) tako da njen &#34;-&#34; terminal bude okrenut prema oznaci &#34;-&#34; na tiskanoj ploči (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW101A50045.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "37.223mm" ver = "01" gw = "130" gh = "89"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite tiskanu ploču u donje kućište i zatim čvrsto pričvrstite gornje kućište.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Iskorištenu bateriju zbrinite pravilno, u skladu s važećim zakonima i propisima. Litijske baterije ne zbrinjavajte s običnim kućanskim otpadom.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
</s1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
